WEBVTT

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:45.670
Well, welcome family. Thank you for

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:48.069
joining us again tonight. We're going to

00:00:48.079 --> 00:00:50.069
just get right to praying. I've been

00:00:50.079 --> 00:00:52.150
really busy lately, and I'm so

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:53.670
thankful for every single one of you.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:56.950
We're fine. I had to take some days.

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.029
The Lord said, 'You need more time

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:01.830
focusing just with me.'And I've

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:03.189
poured out and poured out, and

00:01:03.199 --> 00:01:05.189
I've got to the point

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:07.109
where I feel dry and I said, 'I've got

00:01:07.119 --> 00:01:08.789
to get back underneath that

00:01:08.789 --> 00:01:08.799
waterfall.'It's

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:12.070
personal.

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:14.070
Just because I dump

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:16.230
out with you all doesn't mean I

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:16.240
don't

00:01:16.240 --> 00:01:18.789
keep vertical with him, and I want to

00:01:18.799 --> 00:01:21.670
make sure I'm hearing him in top shape.

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:24.390
Keeping my relationship with him

00:01:24.390 --> 00:01:24.400
above

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:27.350
all this other stuff; it doesn't

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.270
matter to me if it all goes away

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:32.149
tomorrow, I still have him. And that's

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:33.749
what I want to make sure: that we're always

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:35.749
good and that in my heart

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:38.230
I'm seeking his face.

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:40.149
There's so much ministry that pulls you

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:41.749
every single day, and you can get

00:01:41.759 --> 00:01:43.830
distracted with it. Then you've got

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:45.910
family, you've got kids you're raising,

00:01:45.910 --> 00:01:45.920
you've

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:47.590
got a job you're working; there's things

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:49.590
that are always pulling on you. But I have

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:52.069
to make sure that I'm always staying

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:53.670
sharp,

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.030
especially when you're talking to

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:57.590
as many people as we do. And so

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:01.350
I take the time. After the tornado,

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:03.670
I was frustrated with that. We have

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:06.310
power and authority over storms, you

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:09.270
know, and God has given us that.

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:12.150
As he is, so are we in this world.

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:15.350
And as we see tornadoes come and they're

00:02:15.350 --> 00:02:15.360
wreaking

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:18.070
havoc and doing all

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.670
that they're doing and

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:22.630
everybody's afraid,

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:25.430
I warned you all. I said there are storms

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:27.110
coming.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:29.589
It's not just in the natural storms, but

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:32.229
