00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:04.229
activate that inside of you.

00:03:04.229 --> 00:03:04.239
Psalm

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:07.509
91, Psalm 23, getting it down

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:10.070
