00:36:54.000 --> 00:36:56.550
this will be a place of oasis for

00:36:56.560 --> 00:37:00.470
people to come and drink.

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:02.950
But I saw again—and I'll tell you

00:37:02.960 --> 00:37:05.910
this. Last night I had a dream and

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:07.510
I saw a man—I won't tell you who

00:37:07.510 --> 00:37:07.520
he

00:37:07.520 --> 00:37:09.829
was—and

00:37:09.839 --> 00:37:14.069
I was in a Dillard's

00:37:14.079 --> 00:37:17.270
and they were laying hands on people.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:20.230
This main minister was in there and the

00:37:20.240 --> 00:37:22.790
Holy Ghost and fire fell in the

00:37:22.790 --> 00:37:22.800
Dillard's

00:37:22.800 --> 00:37:25.270
store and people were laying out

00:37:25.280 --> 00:37:27.910
everywhere with the power of God falling

00:37:27.920 --> 00:37:29.510
on them, and they were being healed by

00:37:29.520 --> 00:37:31.670
the power of the Lord because a revival

00:37:31.680 --> 00:37:34.870
broke out in Dillard's.

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:37.270
I saw the staff filming with their

00:37:37.280 --> 00:37:38.950
phones.

00:37:38.960 --> 00:37:40.950
They were all filming because it was in

00:37:40.960 --> 00:37:42.790
the shoe department as the people were

00:37:42.800 --> 00:37:44.630
laid out in the Holy Ghost everywhere.

00:37:46.720 --> 00:37:48.950
I walked up to a

00:37:48.950 --> 00:37:48.960
lady—she

00:37:48.960 --> 00:37:51.109
was an African-American

00:37:51.109 --> 00:37:51.119
woman—and

00:37:51.119 --> 00:37:53.670
she said, "I so desperately want

00:37:53.670 --> 00:37:53.680
a

00:37:53.680 --> 00:37:56.390
touch like that. Could somebody help

00:37:56.390 --> 00:37:56.400
me?"And

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:59.430
I said, "Follow me."And I took

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:01.510
her over there and she got baptized in

00:38:01.520 --> 00:38:02.870
the Holy Ghost and fire, and she was

00:38:02.880 --> 00:38:07.910
speaking in tongues and crying

00:38:07.920 --> 00:38:09.750
as the glory touched her in the middle

00:38:09.760 --> 00:38:14.710
of Dillard's.

00:38:14.720 --> 00:38:16.710
We're about to experience something

00:38:16.720 --> 00:38:21.829
that's going to be church unusual.

00:38:21.839 --> 00:38:24.310
Don't have preconceived ideas of how you

00:38:24.320 --> 00:38:28.310
think this next move is going to

00:38:28.310 --> 00:38:28.320
be—that

00:38:28.320 --> 00:38:30.390
it has to be like how Oral Roberts

00:38:30.400 --> 00:38:32.470
did it and Kathryn Kuhlman and all these

00:38:32.480 --> 00:38:37.349
others. Oh, no. Those were old wells.

00:38:37.359 --> 00:38:39.349
The Lord said, "Behold, I'm going to do

00:38:39.359 --> 00:38:41.750
something new."And when I was standing

00:38:41.760 --> 00:38:44.310
there and he said, "Can these bones

00:38:44.320 --> 00:38:46.710
live?

00:38:46.720 --> 00:38:51.430
Speak to the dry

00:38:51.430 --> 00:38:51.440
bones,"I

00:38:51.440 --> 00:38:54.470
saw a wave of the glory of God

00:38:54.480 --> 00:38:56.870
fill the atmosphere of all of these

00:38:56.880 --> 00:38:59.430
churches. And a wave went up even on

00:38:59.440 --> 00:39:01.349
Pastor

00:39:01.359 --> 00:39:03.670
John Kilpatrick's feet; the wave came up on him and

00:39:03.680 --> 00:39:06.870
it overtook

00:39:06.870 --> 00:39:06.880
him—the

00:39:06.880 --> 00:39:08.950
wave of his presence, the wave of the

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:12.470
glory.

00:39:12.480 --> 00:39:15.190
The Lord said it would be. I saw people

00:39:15.200 --> 00:39:17.270
and the glory of the Lord come

00:39:17.280 --> 00:39:20.150
in. You can't move in the service

00:39:20.160 --> 00:39:22.150
because the glory and the presence and

00:39:22.160 --> 00:39:25.990
the shekinah glory is so heavy that

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:27.430
people were crawling out—those were

00:39:27.440 --> 00:39:29.030
sinners who didn't want to be right with the

00:39:29.040 --> 00:39:31.349
Lord.

00:39:31.359 --> 00:39:32.790
Some of them were like, "I've got to get out of

00:39:32.790 --> 00:39:32.800
here,"because

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:33.990
they

00:39:34.000 --> 00:39:35.990
didn't want to give up their sin. But

00:39:36.000 --> 00:39:37.670
God wasn't forcing; He's a gentleman.

00:39:37.680 --> 00:39:38.950
He's not going to force you to serve

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:40.630
Him.

00:39:40.640 --> 00:39:42.710
I

00:39:42.720 --> 00:39:44.390
saw this one individual—I don't know why the

00:39:44.400 --> 00:39:45.670
Lord allowed me to see this one

00:39:45.670 --> 00:39:45.680
individual—but

00:39:45.680 --> 00:39:47.430
they didn't want to be

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:48.550
there. And the Lord said, "Brandon, you

00:39:48.560 --> 00:39:51.910
don't have to be here.

00:39:51.920 --> 00:39:53.829
Even when you show up, I'm not

00:39:53.839 --> 00:39:57.829
going to force you to be there. You have

00:39:57.839 --> 00:40:01.589
a

00:40:01.589 --> 00:40:01.599
choice."He

00:40:01.599 --> 00:40:06.069
doesn't take over your free will; He's

00:40:06.069 --> 00:40:06.079
a

00:40:06.079 --> 00:40:09.109
gentleman. He wants you to want to have a

00:40:09.119 --> 00:40:11.510
relationship with Him. No one is ever

00:40:11.520 --> 00:40:12.870
forced to have a relationship with

00:40:12.880 --> 00:40:15.589
Jesus.

00:40:15.599 --> 00:40:17.270
Just like you don't force your kids to

00:40:17.280 --> 00:40:22.230
have a relationship with you,

00:40:22.240 --> 00:40:24.470
how much more

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:25.910
God wants to have a relationship with

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:28.870
you so bad. I saw the glory of the

00:40:28.880 --> 00:40:31.750
Lord. I saw arms growing out. I've seen

00:40:31.760 --> 00:40:33.990
the blind eyes open. But it

00:40:34.000 --> 00:40:36.069
will be something that we've never felt. A

00:40:36.079 --> 00:40:41.670
breeze, a wind will fill the atmosphere.

00:40:41.680 --> 00:40:44.470
And the Lord said, "You

00:40:44.470 --> 00:40:44.480
see,"and

00:40:44.480 --> 00:40:47.030
I bring it up again: Oral Roberts took a

00:40:47.040 --> 00:40:49.589
cup and this well and he said,

00:40:49.599 --> 00:40:51.190
"The wells of revival are coming

00:40:51.190 --> 00:40:51.200
uncapped."And

00:40:51.200 --> 00:40:54.550
I saw him go down. Jack

00:40:54.550 --> 00:40:54.560
Coe,

00:40:54.560 --> 00:40:57.430
if I mess up his name, forgive me.

00:40:57.440 --> 00:41:00.470
Jack Coe went down and dipped his cup and

00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:02.710
got a little bit of a drink; Oral Roberts got

00:41:02.720 --> 00:41:04.309
a little bit of a drink. But they didn't

00:41:04.319 --> 00:41:05.990
go to the bottom of the well. And the

00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:09.109
Lord said, "This time,

00:41:09.119 --> 00:41:12.390
all

00:41:12.400 --> 00:41:14.309
boundaries,

00:41:14.319 --> 00:41:17.589
all preconceived notions—you're going

00:41:17.599 --> 00:41:18.710
to be able to go in the middle of the

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:24.630
well and go all the way to the

00:41:24.630 --> 00:41:24.640
bottom."This

00:41:24.640 --> 00:41:29.589
is the great finale.

00:41:29.599 --> 00:41:33.030
Are you excited?

00:41:33.040 --> 00:41:35.910
This is the great finale. This is what

00:41:35.920 --> 00:41:38.710
we've all been waiting for,

00:41:38.720 --> 00:41:41.670
and it's here. The Lord says, "Start

00:41:41.680 --> 00:41:44.309
saying it's here."It's not coming; it's

00:41:44.319 --> 00:41:47.750
here. It's time now. Call it forth. It's

00:41:47.760 --> 00:41:49.990
coming out of prayer, but it's not just

00:41:50.000 --> 00:41:52.470
this patty-cake Christianity prayer.

00:41:52.480 --> 00:41:55.430
No, it's getting in the Holy Ghost

00:41:55.440 --> 00:41:58.550
river and pulling with me

00:41:58.560 --> 00:42:00.230
on the chats and all this stuff. I'm

00:42:00.240 --> 00:42:03.030
telling you, it's time. We can pull

00:42:03.040 --> 00:42:06.950
this. It's like

00:42:06.950 --> 00:42:06.960
jumping

00:42:06.960 --> 00:42:09.589
in the river tonight.

00:42:09.599 --> 00:42:13.270
Stir yourself up. Well, if you're

00:42:13.280 --> 00:42:16.950
thirsty, drink.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:20.790
He is the vast supply.

00:42:20.800 --> 00:42:24.309
Come to the water that never runs dry.

00:42:24.319 --> 00:42:27.030
He is that fountain.

00:42:27.040 --> 00:42:29.510
And it's time for you to stir yourself

00:42:29.520 --> 00:42:31.670
up and pray. If you don't know how to

00:42:31.680 --> 00:42:34.230
pray in tongues, stir yourself. And

00:42:34.240 --> 00:42:35.750
He's not going to come and wag your

00:42:35.760 --> 00:42:38.390
tongue for you. You've got to just

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:41.109
say, "Holy Spirit, I yield to

00:42:41.109 --> 00:42:41.119
you,"and

00:42:41.119 --> 00:42:43.910
out of your belly shall flow

00:42:43.920 --> 00:42:47.349
rivers of living water.

00:42:47.359 --> 00:42:49.990
Just let that gusher, that Holy

00:42:50.000 --> 00:42:52.230
Ghost fire, come up out of you. You say,

00:42:52.240 --> 00:42:55.109
"I yield to it by

00:42:55.109 --> 00:42:55.119
faith,"and

00:42:55.119 --> 00:42:56.790
just start praying. I'll pray

00:42:56.800 --> 00:42:58.069
with you. I'll be here, too.

00:42:58.079 --> 00:43:00.150
I'll agree with you.

00:43:00.160 --> 00:43:02.230
But tonight's your night to get baptized

00:43:02.240 --> 00:43:04.390
in the Holy Ghost. He will do it right

00:43:04.400 --> 00:43:06.950
behind that camera right now, in your TV,

00:43:06.960 --> 00:43:08.870
in your car, wherever you're watching.

00:43:08.880 --> 00:43:10.710
He'll touch you with the Holy Ghost and

00:43:10.720 --> 00:43:12.790
fire, and He'll change you from the

00:43:12.800 --> 00:43:15.190
inside out. You'll never be the same

00:43:15.200 --> 00:43:19.190
from this day forward.

00:43:19.200 --> 00:43:21.109
But He's not going to do it for you.

00:43:21.109 --> 00:43:21.119
You've

00:43:21.119 --> 00:43:25.990
got to walk on the water.

00:43:26.000 --> 00:43:27.589
Peter had to walk on the water. "Come to

00:43:27.599 --> 00:43:29.030
me, Peter."And Peter said, "No, you

00:43:29.040 --> 00:43:31.510
come to me. No, come over here. Do

00:43:31.510 --> 00:43:31.520
this."And

00:43:31.520 --> 00:43:34.390
guess what? Peter walked on the

00:43:34.400 --> 00:43:38.069
water.

00:43:38.079 --> 00:43:40.309
I want you tonight just to yield to my

00:43:40.319 --> 00:43:43.510
friend. The Holy Spirit will change

00:43:43.520 --> 00:43:48.710
you.

00:43:48.720 --> 00:43:50.870
I say it again: you're

00:43:50.880 --> 00:43:55.270
running out of time.

00:43:57.280 --> 00:44:00.950
The ark is closing. As it was in

00:44:00.960 --> 00:44:02.710
the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of

00:44:02.720 --> 00:44:05.829
Man returns.

00:44:07.920 --> 00:44:10.630
What

00:44:10.640 --> 00:44:13.990
happened then? The rain began to fall.

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:16.470
The earth began to shake. The water

00:44:16.470 --> 00:44:16.480
came

00:44:16.480 --> 00:44:19.430
up from the deep.

00:44:19.440 --> 00:44:22.550
Within just a matter of time, everything

00:44:22.560 --> 00:44:24.630
changed.

00:44:24.640 --> 00:44:26.309
It's going to happen again.

00:44:28.079 --> 00:44:31.670
Are you on the boat?

00:44:31.680 --> 00:44:33.349
He's not going to flood it again with

00:44:33.359 --> 00:44:34.950
water, folks; it's all going

00:44:34.960 --> 00:44:36.710
to be destroyed by fire. But I'm going

00:44:36.720 --> 00:44:38.309
to tell you, it's going to be similar

00:44:38.309 --> 00:44:38.319
to

00:44:38.319 --> 00:44:39.750
how it all happened. It is

00:44:39.760 --> 00:44:43.430
happening suddenly.

00:44:43.440 --> 00:44:45.109
So I want to ask you tonight, do you

00:44:45.119 --> 00:44:48.950
know my friend?

00:44:48.960 --> 00:44:51.349
If you were to die tonight, the very

00:44:51.359 --> 00:44:53.349
shoes you put on today to go to work,

00:44:53.359 --> 00:44:54.950
the undertaker might be taking them off

00:44:54.960 --> 00:44:57.910
that night.

00:44:57.920 --> 00:45:00.470
No one's promised tomorrow.

00:45:00.480 --> 00:45:07.910
Today is the day of salvation.

00:45:07.920 --> 00:45:09.910
Jesus is at your heart right now and

00:45:09.920 --> 00:45:11.349
He's knocking on the door of your

00:45:11.359 --> 00:45:13.190
heart. He's saying, "Will you let me

00:45:13.200 --> 00:45:16.550
in?"Don't

00:45:16.560 --> 00:45:19.589
turn Him away.

00:45:19.599 --> 00:45:22.790
Tonight's your night to repent and turn

00:45:22.800 --> 00:45:24.790
and come to the Father before it's too

00:45:24.800 --> 00:45:27.910
late.

00:45:27.920 --> 00:45:29.670
No man knows the day or the hour

00:45:29.680 --> 00:45:31.430
when the Son of Man returns, but we can see the

00:45:31.440 --> 00:45:35.589
signs of the times all around us.

00:45:42.240 --> 00:45:45.270
I told you on the 1st of April that it

00:45:45.280 --> 00:45:47.990
would be a time of great acceleration.

00:45:48.000 --> 00:45:50.790
And look around you.

00:45:50.800 --> 00:45:52.710
The Lord said, "The birthing pains will

00:45:52.720 --> 00:45:55.349
now double,

00:45:55.349 --> 00:45:55.359
Brandon."They'll

00:45:55.359 --> 00:45:57.750
double even more when Rosh

00:45:57.750 --> 00:45:57.760
Hashanah

00:45:57.760 --> 00:46:00.710
comes in the fall.

00:46:00.720 --> 00:46:03.589
They'll double, as labor

00:46:03.599 --> 00:46:06.870
pains upon a woman.

00:46:06.880 --> 00:46:09.109
Labor pains don't get better; they get

00:46:09.119 --> 00:46:11.349
worse because the baby's

00:46:11.359 --> 00:46:15.670
coming.

00:46:15.680 --> 00:46:17.430
So tonight, I want to ask you, do you

00:46:17.440 --> 00:46:19.829
know my friend? I want you to get

00:46:19.839 --> 00:46:22.630
real with yourself tonight. Are you all

00:46:22.640 --> 00:46:24.470
in?

00:46:24.480 --> 00:46:26.630
Is He your Lord and personal Savior

00:46:26.640 --> 00:46:28.950
tonight? And tonight, if you're

00:46:28.960 --> 00:46:30.309
watching, you say, "Brandon, would you

00:46:30.319 --> 00:46:32.870
please pray for

00:46:32.870 --> 00:46:32.880
me?"I

00:46:32.880 --> 00:46:35.430
want you to just put in the comment

00:46:35.440 --> 00:46:37.510
section tonight, "Tonight's my night.

00:46:37.520 --> 00:46:39.190
I'm going to be saved. Tonight's my

00:46:39.200 --> 00:46:40.870
night. I'm coming home."You could be

00:46:40.880 --> 00:46:43.589
just like the prodigal. You spent all

00:46:43.599 --> 00:46:45.910
you had. You used to be on fire for the

00:46:45.920 --> 00:46:49.109
Lord. You had everything and

00:46:49.119 --> 00:46:51.430
you turned away from Him. He's never

00:46:51.440 --> 00:46:53.430
turned His back on you; you've turned

00:46:53.440 --> 00:46:55.750
your back on Him. He's an

00:46:55.760 --> 00:46:57.430
ever-present help in a time of need.

00:46:57.440 --> 00:46:59.030
He'll never leave you; He'll never

00:46:59.040 --> 00:47:00.710
forsake you. But you can turn away from

00:47:00.720 --> 00:47:03.190
Him.

00:47:03.200 --> 00:47:05.829
"I don't need you

00:47:05.829 --> 00:47:05.839
anymore,"and

00:47:05.839 --> 00:47:10.870
He'll let you go. A gentleman would.

00:47:10.880 --> 00:47:12.630
But tonight you say, "Brandon, I don't

00:47:12.640 --> 00:47:14.630
want to live this way anymore. I know.

00:47:14.640 --> 00:47:16.870
I can see it. I can feel it as you talk.

00:47:16.880 --> 00:47:23.109
I know something is about to

00:47:23.109 --> 00:47:23.119
happen."And

00:47:23.119 --> 00:47:24.550
tonight's your night to be on the

00:47:24.560 --> 00:47:26.710
right side of it.

00:47:26.720 --> 00:47:28.630
But if Jesus died for you

00:47:28.640 --> 00:47:30.630
publicly, then I want you to be public in

00:47:30.640 --> 00:47:33.109
your decision tonight.

00:47:33.119 --> 00:47:36.390
Put it in the chat: "What must I do to be

00:47:36.400 --> 00:47:37.990
saved? I want to be saved

00:47:37.990 --> 00:47:38.000
tonight."And

00:47:38.000 --> 00:47:39.030
I'm going to pray for you. Just say

00:47:39.040 --> 00:47:41.910
this simple prayer: "Jesus, I

00:47:41.920 --> 00:47:44.790
believe you're the Son of God. I believe

00:47:44.800 --> 00:47:46.630
you died for me and you rose again on

00:47:46.640 --> 00:47:49.349
the third day.

00:47:49.359 --> 00:47:53.430
Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a Savior.

00:47:53.440 --> 00:47:59.190
Forgive me of my sins. Tonight,

00:47:59.200 --> 00:48:02.790
Lord, I turn my back on my sin. I turn

00:48:02.800 --> 00:48:05.510
my back on the devil. I turn my back on

00:48:05.520 --> 00:48:07.990
what I was doing. And from this day

00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:11.030
forward, Lord, I'm sold out to you,

00:48:11.040 --> 00:48:13.270
Jesus. I ask you to write my name in the

00:48:13.280 --> 00:48:15.990
Lamb's Book of Life.

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:18.230
From this day forward, Lord, I belong to

00:48:18.240 --> 00:48:21.349
you. I'll serve you until the end, and

00:48:21.359 --> 00:48:22.870
even on the other side, I'll be in

00:48:22.880 --> 00:48:25.109
heaven with you forever.

00:48:25.119 --> 00:48:26.950
Thank you, Lord, that I'm born

00:48:26.960 --> 00:48:29.750
again tonight. I thank you, Lord,

00:48:29.760 --> 00:48:32.150
that I'm washed in your blood. Thank

00:48:32.160 --> 00:48:34.950
you, Lord, that my sin is gone from me.

00:48:34.960 --> 00:48:37.190
As far as the east is from the west,

00:48:37.200 --> 00:48:39.589
you've taken it from me, Lord, and

00:48:39.599 --> 00:48:40.790
you've cast it in the sea of

00:48:40.800 --> 00:48:42.390
forgetfulness.

00:48:42.400 --> 00:48:44.790
Thank you, Lord, that I'm born again.

00:48:44.800 --> 00:48:46.470
Thank you, Lord, that I'm washed in your

00:48:46.480 --> 00:48:48.950
blood, and I'm so grateful for what you

00:48:48.960 --> 00:48:51.750
did for me. Amen and amen."I believe if

00:48:51.760 --> 00:48:53.510
you just said that simple little prayer

00:48:53.520 --> 00:48:55.750
and you believe that Jesus Christ is the

00:48:55.760 --> 00:48:58.309
Son of God—there's no other way to the

00:48:58.319 --> 00:49:00.230
Father other than through the Lord Jesus

00:49:00.240 --> 00:49:02.150
Christ—then

00:49:02.160 --> 00:49:05.030
welcome to the family.

00:49:05.040 --> 00:49:07.510
So what do you do now?

00:49:07.520 --> 00:49:10.470
I'd go to a Bible-believing church. You get

